OL,3,CChild rapist who fled to Ireland jailed
OL,5,FA man who fled to Ireland after being
OL,6,Ffound guilty of sex offences against
OL,7,Ffour children has been jailed.
OL,9,FJason Spence, 38, went missing after
OL,10,Fbeing bailed by Leeds Crown Court
OL,11,Fhaving been convicted of multiple
OL,12,Foffences, including four rapes,
OL,13,Ffollowing a trial in April.
OL,15,FHe was on the run for 33 days before
OL,16,Fbeing arrested in Ireland and returned
OL,17,Fto the UK.
OL,19,FOn Wednesday Spence was jailed for 24
OL,20,Fyears, with an extended eight-year
OL,21,Flicence period.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
