OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783700376
OL,3,CChild rapist who fled to Ireland jailed
OL,5,FDet Con Susan Abbott, of West
OL,6,FYorkshire Police, said: "Spence has
OL,7,Ftried to evade justice by leaving the
OL,8,Fcountry before he could be sentenced,
OL,9,Fcausing further distress to his
OL,10,Fvictims and their family members.
OL,12,F"We were determined to find him and
OL,13,Fworked closely with Garda to ensure he
OL,14,Fwas arrested and brought back to the
OL,15,FUK to be sentenced.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
