PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783700376
OL,3,CChild rapist who fled to Ireland jailed
OL,5,F"Spence is clearly a dangerous man who
OL,6,Fhas preyed on multiple children. I
OL,7,Fhope that knowing he is now in prison
OL,8,Fhelps those who have been involved in
OL,9,Fthis awful case as they continue to
OL,10,Ftry and rebuild their lives."
OL,12,FSpence, of Roker Lane, Pudsey,
OL,13,Fcommitted offences against children
OL,14,Fwho were all under 13.
OL,16,FHe was also found guilty of making and
OL,17,Fpossessing indecent images of children.
