CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1783700376
OL,3,CChild rapist who fled to Ireland jailed
OL,5,FDet Con Gemma Varley, of Leeds
OL,6,FDistrict Safeguarding, said: "What
OL,7,Fthese children have endured at such a
OL,8,Fyoung age is unimaginable.
OL,10,F"This was a complex investigation that
OL,11,Frequired extremely sensitive handling,
OL,12,Fbalancing the need to gain evidence to
OL,13,Fensure Spence was convicted with being
OL,14,Fcareful and considerate of the trauma
OL,15,Fthat these young victims had already
OL,16,Fbeen exposed to."
OL,26,@nD@^OUrD@AOU
